"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"We‚Äôll use Njalla and Zcash to buy the domain name, and BitLaunch and Etherium to buy a virtual server to get the website online - all without giving up any personal information üôå.\\n\\n### Step 1. Create a Njalla Account\\n\\nNjalla is a ‚Äúprivacy-aware‚Äù domain registrar. Using a traditional domain registrar like GoDaddy to buy a domain like thisismyprivatewebsite.com would [require that you provide](https://www.godaddy.com/agreements/privacy) your ‚Äúname, address, telephone number, date of birth, email address, billing and payment information, and other data collected that could directly or indirectly identify you.‚Äù üò¨\\n\\nIt doesn‚Äôt help that when we give out our personal information [it always seems to get hacked](https://www.pcmag.com/news/godaddy-hacked-12m-customers-at-risk-of-phishing-attack). When you use Njalla, none of that applies. All you need is cryptocurrency. Go to their site and create an account.\\n\\nPublic website: https://njal.la/\\nOnion website: njallalafimoej5i4eg7vlnqjvmb6zhdh27qxcatdn647jtwwwui3nad.onion\\n\\n![Njalla account signup screen](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/bL_I7taLhDRppviZpD8-E.png?height=784&width=1000)\\n\\n### Step 2: Add Funds\\n\\nGo to Account > Wallet > Add Funds\\n\\nNjalla allows you to pay using Zcash, a private cryptocurrency. A premium domain costs around $20 USD per year, so we‚Äôll send that much to our Njalla Wallet. Wait for the transaction to complete before navigating away from this page - I waited 5-10 minutes for the payment to be confirmed.\\n\\n![Zcash payment QR code](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Vkyk7OlffvnUtsUGtjIWz.png?height=784&width=1000)\\n\\n### Step 3: Buy a Domain\\n\\nClick on the ‚ÄúDomains‚Äù tab and search for a domain.\\n\\n![Domain checkout on Njalla](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/065l8zuxMi4QCYaEzSZNC.png?height=784&width=1000)\\n\\nSelect and purchase the domain with the funds that you deposited. When you‚Äôve completed registration you‚Äôll see a success message.\\n\\n![Success message](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/p-DrS7qJy90L1cyFFkSL3.png?height=784&width=1000)\\n\\n### Step 4: Create a BitLaunch Account\\n\\nNow that we have our domain name, we need a host for the website‚Äôs content. We‚Äôll use BitLaunch, a service that allows you to use cryptocurrency to pay for a virtual server. Head over to their site to create an account.\\n\\nPublic website: https://bitlaunch.io\\n\\n![BitLaunch homepage](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/M3M431du_1UjTOKwF0nUO.png?height=784&width=1000)\\n\\n### Step 5: Add Funds\\n\\nBitLaunch allows you to pay with Bitcoin, Etherium, or Litecoin. Deposit as much as you‚Äôd like to get started. I started with $50 USD.\\n\\n![BitLaunch payment screen](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/kmSl7Wm4ZqMJRHgjduT-C.png?height=784&width=1000)\\n\\n### Step 6: Create a Server\\n\\nI chose BitLaunch with a Debian image.\\n\\n![Creating a new server on BitLaunch](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/u9OaE7QHindRUcsSdWIu0.png?height=784&width=1000)\\n\\n### Step 7: Install NGINX\\n\\nWhen you created your server, you also created an SSH login password. Log in to your server and [install NGINX](https://pimylifeup.com/raspberry-pi-nginx/).\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/m9bN3nyXy7sgT2PFmUzJn.png?height=382&width=570)\\n\\n### Step 8: Update Your Domain‚Äôs DNS Settings\\n\\nBack at Njalla on the ‚ÄúDomains‚Äù tab click ‚ÄúManage‚Äù next to your domain.\\n\\n![Njalla \\\"Domains\\\" tab](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/7GBTAmVmFrlRWx3_aAN1k.png?height=784&width=1000)\\n\\nOn the ‚ÄúDNS Settings‚Äù subtab, you‚Äôll see the option to add a new DNS record. In the content field, enter the IP address of your BitLaunch server. Click the ‚Äú+‚Äù button when you‚Äôre done.\\n\\n![Configuring DNS settings on Njalla](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/PkVOtpc1SvfS5BGBrNi6A.png?height=784&width=2113)\\n\\n### Step 9: Visit Your New Website\\n\\nEnter your domain name into your browser and visit your new website!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/xxrq6ri9htQ5h3k1Pz6xh.png?height=784&width=1000)\\n\\nüéâ Congratulations, you just launched a website and kept your ‚Äúname, address, telephone number, date of birth, email address, billing and payment information, and other data collected that could directly or indirectly identify you‚Äù private!\\n\\nQuestions? Follow me on Twitter [@glennsorrentino](https://twitter.com/glennsorrentino).\",\"timestamp\":1638050889,\"title\":\"üöÄ Launch a public website without giving up your personal information\"},\"digest\":\"0ZfS8o-aSlG3kfuEylc58C8_c6JfAJ4HnLBNTb9RLCg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf4A3BBB8560D149C116d67CA5917A186cc13Fe30\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"vWlImahoGYV67vw7XX_VucRpo5RT47X35ofZ0thFCEs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rw6eBnmJo5znIw_IhL7GMo3KW4ULPM4BecOGXXtq2_c\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"uGM6nVd0U0_kR8aRFBHbjZNx0K3BHQlhA4fLSLuxbKW16BtoS5nCuxorWWpZO7LbXMOhrpEfOm6Dh0pnkD7h_A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xebdc05550e7fcc4910ea495855552fb90e42e319474dac78eeabda8b839883d72249ec17e6a81fe9096b5ed26a6d828d52726f905d2d8df424f2846c454a63351c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"vWlImahoGYV67vw7XX_VucRpo5RT47X35ofZ0thFCEs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rw6eBnmJo5znIw_IhL7GMo3KW4ULPM4BecOGXXtq2_c\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"iastUUFjGm0zRLNbxNZvdQobjaOjE1wpGAVvB0fKSOA\"}"